data.description: Cute as can be 1 bedroom bungalow in Westport. Easy commute to historic Astoria, Wauna and Knappa and . Close to ferry, fire station, dining and gas station/market. Updated home features covered front and back porches, bonus/dining room off entry, kitchen with eating area, extra large utility room. Washer, dryer, refrigerator, range and dishwasher included. Enjoy home ownership for less than rent.
